    "Orchestration and management function is used mainly to parse intents and perform business logical orchestration based on intents and schedule domain twin entities to complete twinning tasks, thus ensuring closed-loop iteration.",
    "The NDT service function is the core of the digital twin entity, which is used for twin modeling to achieve simulation and pre-verification.",
    "Three functional units, namely the model construction and management unit, digital twin orchestration unit, and interaction and control unit, have been therefore innovatively proposed to build the core functions of the digital twin entity.",
    "The accuracy and granularity of these units determine the twinning and mapping capabilities of the DTN to the physical network.",
